  "detailed_description": "<h1>Try it before you buy it!</h1><p>You can try our game via the Open Playtest. Just \"Request Access\" above and it will be granted instantly.</p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an exciting adventure of epic proportions inspired by the rich folklore of south-eastern Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this turn-based roguelike card battler, take the role of a miller’s offspring, their life upended during a vicious raid, and shape their place in a war-torn medieval world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find companions to help you overcome adversity, train, collect, and equip your party with better gear to give yourself an edge in the tests ahead. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Fresh Spin on the Deckbuilding Genre</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your equipment and training dictate what cards are available, how many, and how powerful they are. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/88569d2d7311cf567f90eaa30a577546.poster.avif?t=1733413090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/88569d2d7311cf567f90eaa30a577546.webm?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/88569d2d7311cf567f90eaa30a577546.mp4?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We fused dynamic initiative, simple positioning, turn delay, and turn-based card play into a rich and rewarding combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/15e60c2af0e5bde0fe3e7a907f6fcb04.poster.avif?t=1733413090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/15e60c2af0e5bde0fe3e7a907f6fcb04.webm?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/15e60c2af0e5bde0fe3e7a907f6fcb04.mp4?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Varied Card Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not all cards are created equal; some are actions the characters will take during their turn, while others are reactive and must be kept in hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/5932dcf08598f50b49da02e5ca9a5fa1.poster.avif?t=1733413090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/5932dcf08598f50b49da02e5ca9a5fa1.webm?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/5932dcf08598f50b49da02e5ca9a5fa1.mp4?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your party's training to better prepare them for the trials that await them. Only through focused training combined with battle experience will they progress from novices to masters of their weapons of choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your actions will determine how people will remember you. Will they sing heroic ballads in every tavern, or will they whisper tales untold about your infamous exploits?   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only time will tell if your stories will become Unsung Ballads.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an exciting adventure of epic proportions inspired by the rich folklore of south-eastern Europe.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In this turn-based roguelike card battler, take the role of a miller’s offspring, their life upended during a vicious raid, and shape their place in a war-torn medieval world.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find companions to help you overcome adversity, train, collect, and equip your party with better gear to give yourself an edge in the tests ahead. </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >A Fresh Spin on the Deckbuilding Genre</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your equipment and training dictate what cards are available, how many, and how powerful they are. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/88569d2d7311cf567f90eaa30a577546.poster.avif?t=1733413090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/88569d2d7311cf567f90eaa30a577546.webm?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/88569d2d7311cf567f90eaa30a577546.mp4?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Tactical Combat</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We fused dynamic initiative, simple positioning, turn delay, and turn-based card play into a rich and rewarding combat experience.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/15e60c2af0e5bde0fe3e7a907f6fcb04.poster.avif?t=1733413090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/15e60c2af0e5bde0fe3e7a907f6fcb04.webm?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/15e60c2af0e5bde0fe3e7a907f6fcb04.mp4?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Varied Card Play</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not all cards are created equal; some are actions the characters will take during their turn, while others are reactive and must be kept in hand. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/5932dcf08598f50b49da02e5ca9a5fa1.poster.avif?t=1733413090\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/5932dcf08598f50b49da02e5ca9a5fa1.webm?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2366240/extras/5932dcf08598f50b49da02e5ca9a5fa1.mp4?t=1733413090\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Character Progression</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Manage your party's training to better prepare them for the trials that await them. Only through focused training combined with battle experience will they progress from novices to masters of their weapons of choice. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your actions will determine how people will remember you. Will they sing heroic ballads in every tavern, or will they whisper tales untold about your infamous exploits?   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Only time will tell if your stories will become Unsung Ballads.</p>",
